# Yatharth Group of Institution Website

## About Project

This is a responsive educational website created using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

* Welcome Animation
* Responsive Navbar
* Course Section
* Admission Form
* Theme Switcher
* Counter Animation
* Back to Top Button
* Mobile Friendly Design

## Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript
* Font Awesome

## How to Run

1. Download the project.
2. Open the project folder.
3. Run `index.html` using Live Server.

